{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d212e80a64","title":"给董必武的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"aa6a32dc76","index":0,"year":1951,"month":12,"day":4,"articleId":"d212e80a64"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji31","name":"毛泽东全集第31卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/31-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji31":{"comments":[{"id":"6be3fe0070","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"d212e80a64","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"董必武，当时任政务院副总理兼政治法律委员会主任。"},{"id":"b7287db8ec","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"d212e80a64","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指董必武1951年10月18日关于县乡政权建设问题给中共中央华东局第一书记饶激石的信。董必武在信中指出，加强下级政权机关的工作，可以而且应该经由上级政权机关领导着去做；各级党委对各级政权机关的领导，应经过在政权机关中工作的党员来实现，其中如有党员3人以上，应组成党组以保证党的领导。党直接做政权机关的工作是不好的。"},{"id":"b3a402242c","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"d212e80a64","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指董必武1951年12月3日关于县乡政权建设问题给毛泽东的信。信中对他在1951年10月18日关于同一问题给饶激石写信的背景情况作了说明，并对县乡政权建设问题提出了三点意见：一、下级政权机关的建立，党应经过上级政权机关领导着去做比较好些；二、县乡两级建政工作，目前县级建政是关键；三、县乡建政是一件大事，在组织上和思想上都要有充分的准备。"}],"contents":[{"id":"2c112e088c","type":"title","text":"给董必武的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"d212e80a64"},{"id":"6be3fe0070","type":"paragraph","text":"必武同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"d212e80a64"},{"id":"b7287db8ec","type":"paragraph","text":"我认为你给饶淞石同志的信的内容是正确的，可以抄发华东以外客中央局负责同志一阅，促其注意这件事。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"d212e80a64"},{"id":"b3a402242c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"d212e80a64"},{"id":"589de869dc","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月四日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"d212e80a64"},{"id":"8f88514d98","type":"paragraph","text":"可以连同你此信和我答复你的几句话，一起抄发。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"d212e80a64"},{"id":"f5c7a3c40a","type":"paragraph","text":"又及","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"d212e80a64"}],"page":{"id":"a56c5c0205","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"d212e80a64","start":109,"end":109}}}},"__N_SSG":true}